it.polito.dp2.RNS

Interface ParkingAreaReader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IdentifiedEntityReader, PlaceReader

    public interface ParkingAreaReader
extends PlaceReader
    An interface for reading information about a parking area in the RNS system. A parking area is a special case of a place, also characterized by a set of services (e.g. restaurant, toilet, etc.). Each service is simply a string.
